== 考古调查和批判性分析 ==

== 接受 ==
关于花园塚的考古问题时常引发关注，几个学者已经否定这里是耶稣的墓地。<ref>Bargil Pixner, ''Wege des Messias und Stätten der Urkirche'', Giessen/Basel 1991, p. 275. </ref>但是，撇开考古争议，花园塚已成为新教徒朝圣者的热门朝圣地。<ref name="McGowan2015">{{Cite book|title=Ancient and Modern: Anglican Essays on the Bible, the Church and the World|last=McGowan|first=Andrew B.|date=20 May 2015|publisher=Wipf and Stock Publishers|isbn=9781498230988|page=113|language=en}}</ref>圣公会[[圣乔治座堂_(耶路撒冷)|圣乔治座堂]]就位于花园塚几百米外。<ref name="Milton2013">{{Cite book|title=The Riddle and the Knight: In Search of Sir John Mandeville, the World's Greatest Traveler|last=Milton|first=Giles|date=8 October 2013|publisher=[[Farrar,_Straus_and_Giroux|Farrar, Straus and Giroux]]|isbn=9781466807136|page=153|language=en}}</ref>尽管接受位于圣墓教堂的耶稣墓传统地点的真实性并不是任何教派的信条，天主教和东正教朝圣者坚守传统上的说法，忽视花园塚是耶稣墓所在的可能性。

